name: Prospective application ARTICLE 17.  INSURANCE INFORMATION PROTECTION ACT--REPEALED
text:
§431:16-219  Prospective application.  This part shall not apply to any insurer which is insolvent or unable to fulfill its contractual obligations on July 1, 1988. [L 1987, c 347, pt of §2]
Revision Note
  "July 1, 1988" substituted for "the effective date of this code".
